{"tid":1068172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼妹亡命雙騎　太子衝燈Cut六條線　激撞的士","createTime":"2019-03-19T04:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T07:51:34.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d1eac124c8b95cb9826a6cef23f679b887887e","tid":1068172,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>洋妞亡命雙騎 太子衝燈Cut六條線 激撞的士</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Jmb5eM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Jmb5eM&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=1a9dcffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Jmb5eM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/photo/bkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190319124246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190319124246&h=a483429d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係唔怕死？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬧市中玩命？近日有洋妞在太子鬧市踩單車，更罔顧安危衝出十字路口，被的士撞倒，引來網民批評︰「自殺式襲擊」。<br />\n<br />\n片段被上傳至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，只見星期日（17日）有外籍女子滿臉喜悅地在馬路上踩單車，其外籍友人坐在單車後座。<br />\n<br />\n她們騎至太子道西與塘尾道交界時，無視交通燈號，在多架車輛前逆向穿插，有的士見狀立即煞車。惟當她們準備走近旺角消防局時，另一架的士疑因收掣不及，迎面撞倒單車，二人躺在地上。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛認為該舉動瘋狂︰「單車友咁行法真係想自殺」、「以為自己大晒，又唔用吓腦」、「我記得香港踩單車係咪唔畀載客？」、「呢鑊一定要幫的士司機」。"},{"pid":"91da891e32acc516ddc95621958a30e8366a663d","tid":1068172,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/photo/bkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190319124246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190319124246&h=fc9debb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有外籍女子載着同伴在馬路中穿插。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"4b88ff523c233554878b78b4ba5acf0291c85e9b","tid":1068172,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/photo/bkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190319124246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190319124246&h=7db88e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士迎面撞倒單車。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"a68b0130448e7572203caa66aee0941d9cb886ed","tid":1068172,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190319/photo/bkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190319124246\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190319%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190319120831133-0319_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190319124246&h=4ca0b9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二人被撞倒後倒在馬路上。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"e75052012be54ab45f46e27e7c8d5538668006bb","tid":1068172,"uid":11962,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，同支那人一樣討厭"},{"pid":"d11971139a8da4b4d73f2916afc336e190c5f1b8","tid":1068172,"uid":135957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"262dcb46210e46faf56b2ff3b1b61971c20e840a","tid":1068172,"uid":57376,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"香港馬路上玩單車嘅都係垃圾"},{"pid":"3a4c0d080eb11b2374243b785dd2e3034acaf768","tid":1068172,"uid":62,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e75052012be54ab45f46e27e7c8d5538668006bb","tid":1068172,"uid":11962,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，同支那人一樣討厭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔鐘意咩國家嘅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131a5bbda43ac53ae556cece92a863e8bba70f90","tid":1068172,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{